 <name>patTemplate</name>
 <summary>Powerful templating engine.</summary>
 <description>patTemplate is a powerful, non-compiling templating engine, that uses XML tags to divide a document into different parts.
It provides different template types to emulate if/else and switch/case constructs, variable modifiers,
input- and output filters and several more useful features.
 </description>
